content.rendered:
Directed by Sathyan Anthikad.

Written by Iqbal Kuttippuram.

Cast Dulquer Salmaan(Jomon T. Vincent). Mukesh(Vincent). Aishwarya Rajesh(Vaidehi). Jacob Gregory(Mushtaq). Innocent(Palodan (as Innocent Vareed Thekkethala)). Anupama Parameswaran(Catherine (as Anupama Parameshwaran)). Vinu Mohan(Dr. Alphonse Vincent). Shivaji Guruvayoor(Ravunni). Manobala(Perumal). Indu Thampy(Jesly). Muthumani(Lally). Irshad(Joshy) . Chempil Asokan(Patient). Disney James(Tony). Vinod Kedamangalam(Palodan’s Friend). Sethu Lakshmi(Vincent’s Classmate). Ashvin Matthew(David). Malathy G. Menon(Vincent’s Relative). Veenah Naair(Nancy Kurian). Veena Nair(Nancy). Nandu(Jesly’s Father). Rasna(Tessa)

Language Malayalam.

Producers Sethu Mannarkkad.

Production Full Moon Cinema.
